I don't have to go to an English corner.
Well, I went to an English corner once.
bilingual.target: 嗯，我曾经去过一次英语角。

bilingual.source: Theres a pets corner for the younger children.
bilingual.target: 有一个供小孩子玩的宠物角。

bilingual.source: And there's a reading corner in our classroom.
bilingual.target: 我们的教室里有一个阅读角。

bilingual.source: The teacher's desk is in the corner.
At school, we have a special corner.

list.abstract: corner，英语单词，动词、名词，作及物动词的意思是“垄断；迫至一隅；使陷入绝境；把…难住”，作不及物动词的意思是“囤积；相交成角”，作名词的意思是“角落，拐角处；地区，偏僻处；困境，窘境；(Corner)人名；(法)科尔内；(英)科纳”。

yingyinNormal.en: Or the other corner, or the other corner. Or the one that's currently being built in my ass.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者和另一个街角那家，又或者和另另一个街角那家，或者和要建在我的翘臀的那一家。

yingyinNormal.en: A darkness is coming. It will spread to every corner of the land.
yingyinNormal.zh: 黑暗到来了，蔓延到了中土的每个角落。

yingyinNormal.en: All we need is a piece for that corner and we're done. You did good, kid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个角落再放一个，就大功告成了。宝贝，你做的不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Every street corner it seems, is familiar through documentary, movie and song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每一个街角都是纪录片、电影和歌曲的灵感，并且因而被人熟识。

yingyinNormal.en: And you pass by the corner street and you see this new store called Starbucks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有天，你走到街角发现一家新店，星巴克咖啡店。

yingyinNormal.en: You were living with your wife! All this time! Around the corner! Byron Avenue!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你和你妻子一起住! 一直以来都是! 在街角! 拜伦街道!

yingyinNormal.en: Our printing presses were in that corner. That's why the floor dips back there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当时我们的印刷机在那个角落，所以那儿的地板有些下沉。

yingyinNormal.en: Driving the Machine across the country to this last corner of the grid around New York.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把机器从全国各个角落挤到纽约电网范围内。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow, you still have it? I just assumed it was balled up in the corner of a barn somewhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还留着啊？我还以为会急忙中被揉成一团丢到谷仓的某个角落去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, so, we're in France, we're making the toast. Do you see a little bassinet in the corner?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我们会在法国，然后我们会做吐司，有没有小摇篮（与“矮脚长耳猎犬”谐音）在角落里？

yingyinNormal.en: You never know. That's why I ordered us breakfast from the fancy breakfast place on the corner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世事无常啊，所以我的早餐都是在街角那家高级餐厅订的。

yingyinNormal.en: Stand here, on the corner of Broadway and Seventh Avenue, and you stand at the crossroads of the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 广场座落于百老汇和第七大道之间的角落，而您就站在「世界十字路口」(时代广场别名)。

yingyinNormal.en: A mandate to spread our customs, our cultures, our very way of life, to every corner beneath the blue sky.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要将我们的习俗，我们的文化，我们的生活方式，散播到蓝天下每一个角落。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a corner spot, cutting the risk of door-dings in half. It's a mere 28 steps from the building entrance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那车位是在角落，车门被旁车门撞凹的机率少了一半，而走到楼入口处也只需仅仅28步。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I love your neighborhood. There's a great gym right around the corner from your building. That's my gym.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢你住的社区，街角有家很棒的健身房。那是我的健身房。

yingyinNormal.en: New York touches not only the heavens with its mythic skyline, its influence radiates to every corner of the globe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 纽约不仅以神话般的高楼大厦见称，其影响力更遍及世界每一个角落。

yingyinNormal.en: If you'd like, that button on the corner indicate that you would like make more tutorials. And I'll see you guys next time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你喜欢的话，角落里的按钮表示你想要看更多的化妆视频。下次见啦，姐妹们。

yingyinNormal.en: Max, Han said no, and we need that cappuccino maker for our shop if we're ever gonna compete with the Starbucks around the corner.
yingyinNormal.zh: Max Han不答应，我们必须要有卡布奇诺咖啡机，否则就没法和街角的星巴克竞争。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a vast fleet that can move us to every corner of the county. It's also 12 million reasons why we might not get there on time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 道路发达带我们去这个郡的任何角落，但也有1200万个理由让我们迟到。

yingyinNormal.en: The name of the bad road is Entitlement Avenue, and right now, you are on the corner of Entitlement Avenue and All About Me Boulevard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这条崎岖的路名叫权利大道，现在，你正站在权利大道的拐角处，拐过去就是自我大道。
